query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_action_movie_jap_eng FROM aka_name AS an, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND it.info not in ('screenplay-teleplay','votes distribution','LD status of availablility','LD number','birth name','LD number of chapter stops','mpaa','agent address','bottom 10 rank','admissions','LD laserdisc title','LD group genre','top 250 rank','filming dates','LD color rendition','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','languages','budget','goofs') AND n.gender in ('m') AND (n.name like '%B%') AND (mc.note like '%Australia%' OR mc.note like '%Brazil%' OR mc.note like '%Portugal%' OR mc.note like '%UK%') AND (cn.name like '%STX%' OR cn.name like '%Paramount Pictures%' OR cn.name like '%Miramax%') AND (k.keyword like '%dream%' OR k.keyword like '%war%') AND mi.info in ('Macedonian','Swedish','Albanian','Hungarian','Danish','Dari','Persian','Spanish')
